author: Jason Murray | jmurray@syracuse.com
title: What channel number is CBS Sports Network?
text:
Below is the list of channel numbers for CBS Sports Network in the Syracuse area:
Time Warner: Channel 315 (SD & HD) Verizon Fios: Channel 594 (HD) and 94 (SD) DirectTV: Channel 221 (SD & HD) Dish Network: Channel 158 (SD &HD) New Visions: Not available If you live outside the Syracuse area you can use the channel finder at CBS Sports Network in your area.
You can also live stream selected events using CSBSports.com Live Video .
